title: $6,998/mo - 2,846 sq ft - 4 BR/3.5 BA Redwood Shores Home
posting_body: ['This large, updated home is located in the desirable and much sought-after Redwood Shores Community with top-rated schools in the Belmont-Redwood Shores and Sequoia Union School Districts.', 'Redwood Shores is well-known for its many parks and family-friendly community:', '- Tons of space: 2,846 sq.', 'ft. of living space with alarm system (connection to central monitoring system available)', '-Double-paned windows with plantation shutters throughout', '-Large Great Room, blending together the great room with gas fireplace and eat-in kitchen with recessed lighting, quartz countertops, and Thermador appliances', '-Formal living room with gas fireplace', '-Large formal dining room with recessed lighting and chandelier', '-Hardwood floors on both floors with tiled foyer and bathrooms', '-Laundry room with utility sink and washer/dryer included', '-Paved and stamped cemented backyard, perfect for patio table/outdoor entertaining', '-1/2-block to bus stops', '-1.5 short blocks to Marlin Park (no need to cross any streets) with baseball/soccer field, basketball courts, beach area, playground, picnic tables, & BBQ grills', '-< 1/2-mile to Redwood Shores plaza which includes Nob Hill & many other restaurants/local businesses', '-<1/2-mile to Oracle and Electronic Arts', '-Minimum 1 year lease, then month-to-month after 1st year', '-Security deposit: $6,998.00', '-Cleaning deposit: $1,800.00', '-No smoking/drug-use', '-Tenant pays all utilities', '-Renters Insurance required', '-All applicants will be subject to credit/background and reference checks']
